<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.4">
<l>tērāḷum vāḷarakkaṉ teṉṉilaṅkai veñcamattup poṉṟi vīḻa</l>
<l>pōrāḷuñ cilaiyataṉāl porukaṇaikaḷ pōkkuvittā yeṉṟu nāḷum</l>
<l>tārāḷum varaimārpaṉ taṇcēṟai yemperumā ṉumpa rāḷum</l>
<l>pērāḷaṉ pērōtum periyōrai yorukālum piriki lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Daily saying, “You sent battle arrows with a bow used for war</l>
<l rend="indent">in heated combat in Laṅkā of the South</l>
<l>So that the sword[-bearing] demon who uses chariots died, being ruined,”</l>
<l>I cannot part for even one time from the great ones who chant the names</l>
<l>Of the renown one who rules heaven, our great lord of cool Cēṟai,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with a mountain[-like] chest where [he] keeps a garland.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
